    <item>
      <title>New App Update Inbound Soon!</title>
      <pubDate>Tuesday, 12 July 2022</pubDate>
      <description>
	&lt;p&gt;Quality of life improvements for P.E.T. are in the works!&lt;/p&gt;
	&lt;p&gt;A "swipe name to negate ghost" functionality is currently in its final stages. If a ghost name is swiped, it will be negated from the list of possible ghosts. Reswiping the name will remove the negation.&lt;/p&gt;
	&lt;p&gt;This is very useful in certain circumstances, like negating a Wraith after finding footprints.&lt;/p&gt;
	&lt;p&gt;With the Nightmare mode selected, the Moroi will automatically be negated if the Spirit Box is left unselected after two evidence are already confirmed.&lt;/p&gt;
	&lt;p&gt;To help you stay up-to-date, there will soon be Message Center notification icons to alert you of new messages and help you stay up-to-date.&lt;/p&gt;
	&lt;p&gt;Other new features are planned for the end of Summer in seperate installments.&lt;/p&gt;
        &lt;p&gt;Happy Hunting!&lt;/p&gt;
      </description>
    </item>
